title: New: Prehistoric Forest – The Dark Ages
body:
Screw The Strokes, eh? Who needs ’em? This gem from Ocean County’s **Prehistoric Forest** embodies the early 00’s grit of the NY group, alongside a more modern cynicism.

Jagged guitar lines, and Casablanca’s style vocals form the majority of _The Dark Ages_, a track dripping with swagger, sex and the odd flick of sweat. Check it out below.
